How to install Agent
-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=

	1. Unpack the archive (Agent-2.9.tar.gz).

	2. Type 'perl Makefile.PL'.

	3. Run 'make' followed by 'make install'.

	4. Type 'perldoc Agent' to find out
	   how to do things.

	5. Read the Agent.pm module source code.

	6. Read bin/*  it will let you know how to use
	   Agent,  as well as also demonstrating Agentspace.

	7. Write little agents to populate the net.

	8. Give me a backlash,  and tell me how much you hate it, and
	   why -> jduncan@hawk.igs.net - thanks - James.

